text_raw:
2. The 23rd day of May 2022 is appointed as the day on which the 
CervicalCheck Tribunal Act 2019 (No. 31 of 2019) shall, in so far as it is not 
already in operation, come into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

18 May, 2022. 

STEPHEN DONNELLY, 
Minister for Health. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 20th May, 2022.

text_raw:
EXPLANATORY NOTE 

(This note is not part of the Instrument and does not purport to be a legal 
interpretation) 

This Order appoints the 23rd day of May 2022 as the date on which the provisions 
of the CervicalCheck Tribunal Act 2019 that are not already commenced, come 
into operation.
